<p begin="26020000t" end="41260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle0">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="42370000t" end="75020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle1">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="76070000t" end="144790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle2">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="261920000t" end="305260000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle3">&#x202a;果實宣告了未知的將來&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="306300000t" end="374330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle4">&#x202a;夢想蛻變成理想&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="417080000t" end="501380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle5">&#x202a;任誰都渴望落幕…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="518510000t" end="534430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle6">&#x202a;在無垠的黑暗中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="535530000t" end="567840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle7">&#x202a;交換革命的誓言&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="568900000t" end="620550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle8">&#x202a;絕不讓任何人阻撓&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="621620000t" end="670650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle9">&#x202a;總有一天我會讓你看到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="671670000t" end="735040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle10">&#x202a;光輝閃耀的世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="813140000t" end="852160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle11">&#x202a;名字被寫在&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這本筆記本上的人會死&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="875200000t" end="911150000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle12">&#x202a;求求你們住手!&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;好了,結果如何呢?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="941600000t" end="965600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle13">&#x202a;名副其實的…死亡筆記本&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1023350000t" end="1047350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle14">&#x202a;使用過死亡筆記本的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1048380000t" end="1076360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle15">&#x202a;千萬別認為自己&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;可以上天堂或下地獄&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1086410000t" end="1121330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle16">&#x202a;我要讓全世界的人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;知道我的存在&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1122450000t" end="1147360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle17">&#x202a;知道有個正義使者在制裁壞人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1156480000t" end="1167060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle18">&#x202a;而我即將…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1181180000t" end="1196760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle19">&#x202a;成為新世界的神&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1203200000t" end="1229480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle20">&#x202a;第2話 對決&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1235230000t" end="1267880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle21">&#x202a;He Was over floocled&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;With satisfaction…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1268930000t" end="1298620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle22">&#x202a;完全不知道他在想什麼&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;我死心了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1299630000t" end="1309870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle23">&#x202a;真的嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1310970000t" end="1331220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle24">&#x202a;之後和那個老頭怎麼了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1332330000t" end="1349960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle25">&#x202a;那麼夜神同學&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1351010000t" end="1374330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle26">&#x202a;請把剛才的文章翻譯一下&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1375370000t" end="1384010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle27">&#x202a;好的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1414740000t" end="1443410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle28">&#x202a;他的夢想終於成真&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1444440000t" end="1493130000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle29">&#x202a;夢想實現後&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;他沉浸在無比的喜悅中&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1502500000t" end="1516150000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle30">&#x202a;翻譯的很好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1517180000t" end="1535830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle31">&#x202a;不愧是夜神同學&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1536860000t" end="1552440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle32">&#x202a;回答得非常完美&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1588580000t" end="1615880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle33">&#x202a;那麼今天就上到這裡了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1678670000t" end="1718600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle34">&#x202a;終於下課了嗎…&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;學校這種地方真是無聊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1728390000t" end="1737370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle35">&#x202a;喂,月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1744400000t" end="1764650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle36">&#x202a;月,你聽到了嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1765760000t" end="1781000000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle37">&#x202a;別跟我說話&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1782110000t" end="1814420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle38">&#x202a;我的聲音和你不一樣&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;其他的人也會聽得到&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1823820000t" end="1834740000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle39">&#x202a;真是無聊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1839830000t" end="1877140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle40">&#x202a;月,要不要和我們一起…&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;不好意思,我還有事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1893220000t" end="1911530000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle41">&#x202a;你根本沒有事吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1912570000t" end="1944880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle42">&#x202a;你會和平常一樣直接回家吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1945940000t" end="1973920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle43">&#x202a;你在說什麼,我有事情&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="1974970000t" end="2003640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle44">&#x202a;沒錯,非常重要的事情&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2020350000t" end="2059030000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle45">&#x202a;山田嫌犯昨天在新宿區&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;歌舞技叮的餐飲店裡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2060050000t" end="2124670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle46">&#x202a;使用店裡長度約12公分的刀子&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;刺傷同事的腹部&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2130120000t" end="2138420000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle47">&#x202a;喂&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2149140000t" end="2163810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle48">&#x202a;喂,月&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2164820000t" end="2173800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle49">&#x202a;什麼事?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2181840000t" end="2204480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle50">&#x202a;你還真是拚命呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2205530000t" end="2225780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle51">&#x202a;因為我不能浪費時間&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2233230000t" end="2266900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle52">&#x202a;能在筆記本上&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;寫名字的時間有限&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2267930000t" end="2297850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle53">&#x202a;只有放學回來&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;到睡覺前的時間&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2298960000t" end="2333540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle54">&#x202a;讓成績維持名列前茅也很重要&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2334660000t" end="2357300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle55">&#x202a;也不能在上課時打瞌睡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2358350000t" end="2385650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle56">&#x202a;在家裡或補習班&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;也得好好唸書才行&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2392390000t" end="2431070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle57">&#x202a;而且睡眠不足&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;會影響健康與思考能力&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2438760000t" end="2478120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle58">&#x202a;因為我可是要將這個世界&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;變成沒有罪惡的理想世界&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2479140000t" end="2498480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle59">&#x202a;時間再多也不夠&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2520510000t" end="2555780000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle60">&#x202a;怪了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;哥哥你為什麼將房門鎖上&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2561890000t" end="2583500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle61">&#x202a;粧裕嗎?怎麼了?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2584580000t" end="2599820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle62">&#x202a;教我功課&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2608600000t" end="2623270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle63">&#x202a;嗯,好啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2657320000t" end="2685990000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle64">&#x202a;是數學的二次函數&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2687010000t" end="2711010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle65">&#x202a;抱歉打擾你唸書了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2712040000t" end="2741390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle66">&#x202a;但是我真的完全搞不懂&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2742400000t" end="2754340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle67">&#x202a;拜託你了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2755410000t" end="2767010000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle68">&#x202a;好啦好啦&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2768090000t" end="2785720000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle69">&#x202a;月,小心點&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2793120000t" end="2844430000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle70">&#x202a;如果有人碰到抽屜裡的筆記本&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就能看到我了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2858520000t" end="2903120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle71">&#x202a;這麼重要的事情現在才說&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這個死神真是…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2904230000t" end="2925500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle72">&#x202a;哥哥,怎麼了?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2926590000t" end="2937510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle73">&#x202a;沒事&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2938600000t" end="2970910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle74">&#x202a;好了,什麼地方不懂呢?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="2971960000t" end="3001310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle75">&#x202a;我看看,就是…全部不懂&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3012670000t" end="3049640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle76">&#x202a;這一個禮拜就已經知道有52人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3050710000t" end="3072660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle77">&#x202a;全都死於心臟麻痺&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3073730000t" end="3127090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle78">&#x202a;而且都是通緝中或者是&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;拘留在看守所裡面的罪犯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3128120000t" end="3166120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle79">&#x202a;好像還有一些罪犯死亡的消息&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;還沒得到證實&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3167160000t" end="3192070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle80">&#x202a;這麼說至少有100個人以上嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3234230000t" end="3257890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle81">&#x202a;已經開始了喔,局長&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3258920000t" end="3290200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle82">&#x202a;嗯,剛剛總部有事情找我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3291280000t" end="3332920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle83">&#x202a;可是每一個都是&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;應該被判死刑的犯人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3333990000t" end="3351620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle84">&#x202a;所以應該沒關係吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3352680000t" end="3363940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle85">&#x202a;別傻了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3365020000t" end="3403020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle86">&#x202a;不管是重犯還是死囚&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;只要殺了他們就是殺人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3404060000t" end="3431360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle87">&#x202a;又還沒決定是他殺吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3432420000t" end="3465070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle88">&#x202a;100個多人都死於心臟麻痺&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;會有這麼巧的事嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3466120000t" end="3482040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle89">&#x202a;這當然是他殺&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3483140000t" end="3529100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle90">&#x202a;有可能同時在這麼大的範圍裡&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;進行殺人嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3530190000t" end="3573880000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle91">&#x202a;在我看來是龐大組織&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;計劃性的殺人手法&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3574900000t" end="3632920000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle92">&#x202a;說到龐大組織&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;大概也只有FBI或是CIA了吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3633960000t" end="3649540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle93">&#x202a;有種你再說一次&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3650640000t" end="3679650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle94">&#x202a;別吵了,請不要亂開玩笑&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3680670000t" end="3720600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle95">&#x202a;首先要釐清的就是&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這是他殺或是巧合吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3721710000t" end="3743320000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle96">&#x202a;但是根據檢驗報告&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3744400000t" end="3771020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle97">&#x202a;所有人都是死於&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;原因不明的心臟麻痺吧?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3772100000t" end="3816470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle98">&#x202a;從心臟麻痺這個死因進行調查&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;也找不出什麼蛛絲馬跡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3817480000t" end="3856840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle99">&#x202a;真是傷腦筋&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;如果是用刀子刺傷還有跡可尋&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3865860000t" end="3900220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle100">&#x202a;既然如此,只能請L來解決了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3973300000t" end="3997980000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle101">&#x202a;局長,L是誰?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="3998990000t" end="4034600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle102">&#x202a;對了,你是第一次參加這個會議&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4035690000t" end="4084040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle103">&#x202a;沒人知道L的姓名及住處&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4085080000t" end="4124670000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle104">&#x202a;但是再困難的案件他都能解決&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4125780000t" end="4175720000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle105">&#x202a;也解決過全球許多無頭公案&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;是這世界的第一把交椅&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4176830000t" end="4205160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle106">&#x202a;是我們最後的王牌…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4215210000t" end="4273910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle107">&#x202a;但是聽說L是個傲慢人物&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;只願意處理自己有興趣的案件&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4274930000t" end="4285850000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle108">&#x202a;正是如此&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4286940000t" end="4312540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle109">&#x202a;而且我們也無法聯絡上他&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4318310000t" end="4338900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle110">&#x202a;L已經開始行動了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4457780000t" end="4497140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle111">&#x202a;L已經開始調查這件事了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4498160000t" end="4512830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle112">&#x202a;渡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4513840000t" end="4530790000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle113">&#x202a;什麼,渡?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4531860000t" end="4562800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle114">&#x202a;他是唯一能聯絡上L的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4563890000t" end="4594830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle115">&#x202a;不過也沒人知道渡的真實身份&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4595920000t" end="4640860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle116">&#x202a;請大家安靜點&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;現在就讓大家聽聽L的聲音&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4681000000t" end="4729350000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle117">&#x202a;ICPO的各位,我是L&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4747070000t" end="4803390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle118">&#x202a;月,你偷偷摸摸的&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;來這種地方做什麼啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4804460000t" end="4847120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle119">&#x202a;你不是說碰到死亡筆記本的人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就能看到你&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4848170000t" end="4885140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle120">&#x202a;這麼危險的東西怎麼能隨便擺呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4886210000t" end="4918520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle121">&#x202a;我一直認為&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就算被家人發現筆記本&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4919580000t" end="4958600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle122">&#x202a;我可以說「我想當刑警」&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;「所以在學習記錄案件」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4959620000t" end="4983280000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle123">&#x202a;來蒙騙過去&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="4984310000t" end="5013660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle124">&#x202a;原來我這種想法根本是在玩命&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5014670000t" end="5049590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle125">&#x202a;如果有個萬一,說不定我會…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5050710000t" end="5069360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle126">&#x202a;殺了自己的家人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5145140000t" end="5183140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle127">&#x202a;這個案件的困難度&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;不是以往所能相比的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5184170000t" end="5245490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle128">&#x202a;而且絕對不能縱容&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這種殘忍的殺人案件&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5246570000t" end="5292190000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle129">&#x202a;為了解決這件案子&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;請ICPO的各位務必…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5293280000t" end="5344250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle130">&#x202a;不,要請全世界所有的機關&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;來協助我們&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5345340000t" end="5370020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle131">&#x202a;希望此提案&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;能在會議上一致通過&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5371030000t" end="5419380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle132">&#x202a;還有…&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;特別要請日本警察大力協助&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5428080000t" end="5447080000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle133">&#x202a;為…為什麼是日本呢?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5454440000t" end="5510760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle134">&#x202a;不管犯人是團體或是單獨一人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;是日本人的可能性很高&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5517840000t" end="5550830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle135">&#x202a;就算不是日本人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;也是潛伏在日本&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5551870000t" end="5564840000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle136">&#x202a;你有什麼根據?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5571890000t" end="5592480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle137">&#x202a;至於為什麼是日本&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5593580000t" end="5638860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle138">&#x202a;我想最近&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就能看到我跟犯人正面交手了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5645970000t" end="5666220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle139">&#x202a;正面交手?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5667320000t" end="5703270000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle140">&#x202a;總之請把搜查總部設在日本吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5761750000t" end="5779040000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle141">&#x202a;沒想到這麼簡單就完成了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5790450000t" end="5813770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle142">&#x202a;你是說把筆記本藏起來嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5814800000t" end="5839480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle143">&#x202a;是啊,就在這抽屜裡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5849510000t" end="5879200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle144">&#x202a;這樣叫藏起來嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5880200000t" end="5899540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle145">&#x202a;鑰匙還韶在上面呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5900560000t" end="5911480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle146">&#x202a;這樣就好了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5918910000t" end="5953490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle147">&#x202a;應該說鑰匙要刻意&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;放在明顯的位置比較好&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="5980640000t" end="6002590000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle148">&#x202a;不是只有普通的日記嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6003660000t" end="6023340000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle149">&#x202a;我想大多數的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6024350000t" end="6072700000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle150">&#x202a;看到這本日記&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就覺得自己知道抽屜裡的秘密了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6073730000t" end="6084310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle151">&#x202a;不過&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6085410000t" end="6114760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle152">&#x202a;真正的鑰匙是這個&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6115770000t" end="6151380000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle153">&#x202a;就算放在我身邊&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;也不會有人覺得奇怪&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6152470000t" end="6167370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle154">&#x202a;普通的原子筆&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6168490000t" end="6182480000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle155">&#x202a;用它的筆心&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6183510000t" end="6202160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle156">&#x202a;那就是鑰匙嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6203190000t" end="6210810000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle157">&#x202a;沒錯&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6211870000t" end="6257490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle158">&#x202a;抽屜的背面有個&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;要仔細看才能看到的小孔&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6258580000t" end="6274500000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle159">&#x202a;將筆心插入小孔的話…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6322980000t" end="6349600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle160">&#x202a;原來如此,有兩個底板嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6350670000t" end="6389690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle161">&#x202a;不過還有日記這個偽裝物&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;應該就不會被發現吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6390710000t" end="6401970000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle162">&#x202a;還不只是這樣&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6415070000t" end="6472410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle163">&#x202a;就算知道有兩層底板&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;也沒辦法就這樣拿到筆記本&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6490810000t" end="6502070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle164">&#x202a;你懂嗎?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6503160000t" end="6540470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle165">&#x202a;這根原子筆的筆心是絕緣體&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;電流是無法通過的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6541530000t" end="6562460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle166">&#x202a;它能阻斷電流&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6563550000t" end="6580160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle167">&#x202a;將中間的底板關上的時候&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6581240000t" end="6612870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle168">&#x202a;這橡膠就是阻斷電流的絕緣體&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6613940000t" end="6655240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle169">&#x202a;但如果有人硬是要拆掉&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;第二塊板子的話…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6656310000t" end="6693620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle170">&#x202a;瞬間就會點燃&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;裝在超薄塑膠袋裡的汽油&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6712030000t" end="6732960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle171">&#x202a;筆記本就會燒掉了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6734060000t" end="6767050000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle172">&#x202a;這是能完全消滅證據的機關&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6786780000t" end="6799060000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle173">&#x202a;之後可以解釋成&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6800120000t" end="6835730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle174">&#x202a;「不想被人看到」&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;「藏在裡面的真正日記」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6836830000t" end="6862770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle175">&#x202a;這種符合人性的藉口一定能過關&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6863850000t" end="6878180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle176">&#x202a;而且它本來就是筆記本&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6890880000t" end="6913520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle177">&#x202a;我聽說人類得到死亡筆記本時&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6914570000t" end="6954160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle178">&#x202a;最傷腦筋的&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就是不知該藏在哪裡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6955280000t" end="6966200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle179">&#x202a;但是會做到這種地步的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="6967290000t" end="7001870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle180">&#x202a;月,我想你是第一個吧&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7002990000t" end="7033250000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle181">&#x202a;話說回來,這些機關挺危險的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7034360000t" end="7075660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle182">&#x202a;弄錯一個步驟&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;可能會把自己燒成重傷喔&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7076730000t" end="7108360000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle183">&#x202a;危險?路克,你這麼說太奇怪了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7116770000t" end="7146690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle184">&#x202a;我不是早就冒著生命危險了嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7147800000t" end="7169070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle185">&#x202a;從我得到死亡筆記本的那一刻起&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7177830000t" end="7215830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle186">&#x202a;跟那比起來,這根本算不上危險&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7216870000t" end="7241210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle187">&#x202a;應該說是保護我的安全&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7253240000t" end="7280200000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle188">&#x202a;家裡發生小火災&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;和被判死刑&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7281270000t" end="7299240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle189">&#x202a;你說哪個危險呢?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7300620000t" end="7325650000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle190">&#x202a;(寫完名字後在人間界單位40秒內寫死因)&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;(對方就會依此方式死亡)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7325650000t" end="7348970000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle191">&#x202a;(不寫死因的話)&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;(就會因心臟麻痺而死)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7357350000t" end="7402290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle192">&#x202a;(寫完死因後有6分44秒的時間)&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;(可以記述更詳細的死亡過程)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7417410000t" end="7441750000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle193">&#x202a;昨晚在東京都西看守所內&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7442760000t" end="7494410000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle194">&#x202a;一名因犯下搶案入獄服刑的&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;32歲受刑人,黑塚山直鬼&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7495480000t" end="7519820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle195">&#x202a;突然心臟麻痺死亡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7520840000t" end="7561110000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle196">&#x202a;最近發生一連串&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;受刑人因心臟麻痺死亡的情況&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7562220000t" end="7589520000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle197">&#x202a;好棒,壞人一個一個都死了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7590580000t" end="7613900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle198">&#x202a;雖然有點可怕,但也覺得挺爽的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7614940000t" end="7636550000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle199">&#x202a;但以後就不能做壞事了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7637630000t" end="7658220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle200">&#x202a;是不是警察幹的呢?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7659310000t" end="7679900000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle201">&#x202a;警察沒有那種能力啦&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7681000000t" end="7697950000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle202">&#x202a;你不知道嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7699020000t" end="7711640000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle203">&#x202a;什麼東西?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7712700000t" end="7734310000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle204">&#x202a;就是KIRA啊,KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7735390000t" end="7755070000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle205">&#x202a;不知道下一個被殺的是誰呢&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7816140000t" end="7830470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle206">&#x202a;你看看,路克&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7844830000t" end="7868490000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle207">&#x202a;甚至有人架設了這樣的網站&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7887540000t" end="7907220000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle208">&#x202a;救世主KIRA傳說…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7908230000t" end="7923470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle209">&#x202a;挺酷的嘛&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7924580000t" end="7938910000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle210">&#x202a;這是在說你嗎&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7939930000t" end="7949820000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle211">&#x202a;是啊&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7950940000t" end="7980290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle212">&#x202a;好像是借用英文的「殺手」&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;取名「KIRA」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="7981300000t" end="8001890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle213">&#x202a;雖然我不太喜歡&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8002990000t" end="8028930000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle214">&#x202a;但是我已經成為&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;這個世界的KIRA了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8036690000t" end="8076620000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle215">&#x202a;光是用KIRA兩個字搜尋&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就有這麼多的相關網站&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8085070000t" end="8102020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle216">&#x202a;報紙跟電視台&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8103090000t" end="8147690000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle217">&#x202a;現在還是只敢提到&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;「罪大惡極的犯人一一暴斃」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8148800000t" end="8211830000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle218">&#x202a;但是全世界的人都感覺到了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;世上有正義使者在制裁壞人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8235220000t" end="8262180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle219">&#x202a;路克,人類就是這樣的生物&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8273590000t" end="8302940000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle220">&#x202a;例如學校的班會&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8303960000t" end="8344230000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle221">&#x202a;就不會出現&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;「可以殺掉壞人嗎」這樣的議題&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8345330000t" end="8381960000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle222">&#x202a;但是如果有這樣的議題&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;大家都會裝成好孩子&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8383040000t" end="8403290000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle223">&#x202a;不能這麼做&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8404390000t" end="8422020000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle224">&#x202a;大家都會這麼說&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8423080000t" end="8452090000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle225">&#x202a;當然,這樣回答也是對的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8453110000t" end="8504760000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle226">&#x202a;因為人類在公開場合&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;就是必須做表面功夫&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8505830000t" end="8527100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle227">&#x202a;但是內心卻是這麼想的&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8528180000t" end="8573460000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle228">&#x202a;雖然心裡會害怕&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;大家表面上並不承認我這個人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8574560000t" end="8624160000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle229">&#x202a;也不知是誰寫了這些網路文章&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;但是KIRA的名字已經傳開來了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8635620000t" end="8674300000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle230">&#x202a;雖然不能掛在嘴上&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;大家已經都知道了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8675330000t" end="8697630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle231">&#x202a;有人在消滅壞人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8703690000t" end="8757390000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle232">&#x202a;然後沒有做壞事的人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;在心中大喊著「KIRA加油」&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8758410000t" end="8798680000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle233">&#x202a;做了壞事的人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;則是擔心自己會遭到報應&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8814470000t" end="8855770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle234">&#x202a;這樣就好了&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;目前還算是照計劃進行&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8861180000t" end="8878470000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle235">&#x202a;(臨時插播特別新聞)&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8885200000t" end="8900440000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle236">&#x202a;不好意思,節目必須暫停&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8901550000t" end="8957180000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle237">&#x202a;ICPO國際刑警組織&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;要對全世界做同步轉播&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8958280000t" end="8966240000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle238">&#x202a;什麼?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8973630000t" end="8984890000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle239">&#x202a;國際刑警組織?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="8991640000t" end="9002560000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle240">&#x202a;那麼開始了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9018000000t" end="9062370000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle241">&#x202a;我是唯一能調動全球警察的人&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="9063380000t" end="9075660000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle242">&#x202a;LIND·L·TAILOR&#x202c;</p>
