<p begin="12072060000t" end="12107330000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle328">&#x202a;把你送上死刑台&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;的日子或許不遠了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12108420000t" end="12137770000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle329">&#x202a;真厲害,L果然名不虛傳&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12138790000t" end="12169730000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle330">&#x202a;是啊,他證明了KIRA的存在…&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;及殺人事實&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12170820000t" end="12197100000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle331">&#x202a;而且還證明他就在日本&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12206860000t" end="12218800000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle332">&#x202a;KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12219870000t" end="12267540000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle333">&#x202a;我對你用什麼方法來殺人&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;很感興趣&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12268580000t" end="12307600000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle334">&#x202a;但是等到抓到你&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;自然就能知道了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12318300000t" end="12343210000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle335">&#x202a;那麼改天見了,KIRA&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12446430000t" end="12490120000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle336">&#x202a;要把我送上死刑台?&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12508490000t" end="12541140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle337">&#x202a;很有趣,我就接受你的挑戰&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12555870000t" end="12597170000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle338">&#x202a;彼此都不知道長相與名字&#x202c;<br/>&#x202a;還要找出對方…&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12598250000t" end="12628510000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle339">&#x202a;而且先被找到的人就出局了&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="12634620000t" end="12663630000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle340">&#x202a;人類果然很有趣&#x202c;</p>
