<p begin="13517500000t" end="13540140000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle358">&#x202a;要找出L的人不是我&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13541190000t" end="13560870000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle359">&#x202a;警方會查出L的下落&#x202c;</p>
<p begin="13561880000t" end="13589860000t" region="region0" style="style0" tts:extent="80.00% 80.00%" tts:origin="10.00% 10.00%" xml:id="subtitle360">&#x202a;然後我就會除掉L&#x202c;</p>
